(736, 47, 'central_text_description1', 'For AERIS every project is unique. We were impressed by how they listened and worked out a solution that was the best for the project and our business. I found the\r\n        joint working environment very pleasant and every AERIS employee was extremely competent and flexible. This is what we value in project partners!.'),
(737, 47, '_central_text_description1', 'field_620d22f25c73c'),
(738, 47, 'person_name1', 'FABRIZIO TOLLIN'),
(739, 47, '_person_name1', 'field_620d233bcf8e4'),
(740, 47, 'image-slide2', '124'),
(741, 47, '_image-slide2', 'field_620d2365396a5'),
(742, 47, 'central_text_description2', 'From the very beginning of our project with AERIS, it was evident that wed joined forces with a highly professional team that brought enormous innovative potential. Each and every challenge we presented was met with a meticulously thought-through solution. AERIS not only provided us with the most advanced IoT microservices platform for equipment tracking in Europe, their specialists also shared their knowledge and expertise with our own internal IT team, helping them gain new skills and methodologies, such as Agile and DevOps, for our further future success. AERIS helped us create a solution that has propelled us a decade ahead of our competitors.'),
(743, 47, '_central_text_description2', 'field_620d237f396a6'),
(744, 47, 'person_name2', 'THOMAS KONIAREK'),
(745, 47, '_person_name2', 'field_620d2394396a7'),
(746, 47, 'image-slide3', '125'),
(747, 47, '_image-slide3', 'field_620d23a9396a8'),
(748, 47, 'central_text_description3', 'AERIS was a great support with the further development of our platform. Their employees work practices were professional and their knowledge was solid. AERISs expertise gave our project important insights, and we learned to correctly evaluate new market trends. Communication was open and honest, so we reached our goals without detours.'),
(749, 47, '_central_text_description3', 'field_620d23c3396a9'),
(750, 47, 'person_name3', 'YANN LESCURAT'),
(751, 47, '_person_name3', 'field_620d23d7396aa'),
(752, 47, 'image-slide4', '119'),
(753, 47, '_image-slide4', 'field_620d23e9396ab'),
(754, 47, 'central_text_description4', 'Professionalism and competence come first to mind when I think of AERIS. They found a solution that aligned exactly with what our company needed. Everything worked as it should, right from the very beginning. It was a truly perfect fit.'),
(755, 47, '_central_text_description4', 'field_620d23ff396ac'),
(756, 47, 'person_name4', 'ANNA PUTZ'),
(757, 47, '_person_name4', 'field_620d2419396ad'),
(758, 47, 'image-slide5', '120'),
(759, 47, '_image-slide5', 'field_620d242b396ae'),
(760, 47, 'central_text_description5', 'Weve been working with AERIS for many years. There are a number of reasons for this but I want to highlight three: ingenuity, their many years of experience in agile software development and the highly specialized competences of each of their employees. Even in critical situations, AERIS remains focused. This attitude ensures each project is a success.'),
(761, 47, '_central_text_description5', 'field_620d244a396af'),
(762, 47, 'person_name5', 'BRIGITTE AMMANN'),
(763, 47, '_person_name5', 'field_620d245c396b0'),
(764, 47, 'image-slide6', '123'),
(765, 47, '_image-slide6', 'field_620d246d396b1'),
(766, 47, 'central_text_description6', 'Weve cultivated a fantastic joint working environment based on our partnership with AERIS. Their winning combination of extensive specialist knowledge and high competency in a broad range of IT methods leads to quick and efficient solutions in all project phases.'),
